item.description: jQuery jQuery is a fast, small, and feature-rich JavaScript library. For information on how to get started and how to use jQuery, please see jQuery’s documentation. For source files and issues, please visit the jQuery repo. If upgrading, please see the blog post for 3.4.1. This includes notable differences from the previous version and a more readable changelog.
